# Architecture

See `.cursor/rules/foundations/engineering.mdc` for universal principles.

Quick reference:

- Route screens in `web/src/pages/`; reusable UI in `web/src/components/ui/`.
- Data fetching and mutations in `web/src/hooks/`; Supabase client and types in `web/src/lib/`.
- Pages compose components and hooks; business rules live in hooks and `lib/` utilities.
- Shared UI in `web/src/components/ui/common/`; domain UI in `web/src/components/ui/<domain>/`.
- Cross-cutting concerns (theme, routes, constants) in `web/src/lib/` and `web/src/styles/`.
